msgid "Event loop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../glossary/event_loop.rst:5
msgid ""
"Drawing inspiration from modern web frameworks like `React.js "
"<https://reactjs.org/>`_, the Lightning App runs all flows in an **event "
"loop** (forever), which is triggered several times a second after "
"collecting any works' state change."
msgstr ""

#: ../../glossary/event_loop.rst:9
msgid ""
"When running a Lightning App in the cloud, the ``LightningWork`` run on "
"different machines. LightningWork communicates any state changes to the "
"**event loop** which re-executes the flow with the newly-collected works'"
" state."
msgstr ""

